00:45:33,939 --> 00:45:36,150
No, put your one hand up, not both hands.

822
00:45:36,233 --> 00:45:38,026
-Peng Hi!
-Peng Hi!

823
00:45:38,110 --> 00:45:39,903
That's very good.
