00:46:21,862 --> 00:46:22,905
The championship!

838
00:46:23,864 --> 00:46:25,324
Go, Kang Doo-ki!

839
00:46:26,283 --> 00:46:27,326
Go, Kang Doo-ki!

840
00:46:28,785 --> 00:46:30,120
That was very cool.

841
00:46:30,913 --> 00:46:32,664
Kang Doo-ki, when you say it,

842
00:46:32,748 --> 00:46:34,583
it sounds you'll really win
the championship.

