have a place for you in the Dreams.

850
00:47:00,192 --> 00:47:01,276
Have some wits, Chang-ju!

851
00:47:16,667 --> 00:47:17,543
Mr. Baek.

852
00:47:47,990 --> 00:47:49,658
-What's wrong with her?
-She's fast.

853
00:47:49,741 --> 00:47:51,326
Where are you going, Ms. Lee?

854
00:48:18,604 --> 00:48:19,521
Mr. Baek.

855
00:48:21,398 --> 00:48:23,233
Why did you take out all your stuff?

856
00:48:26,236 --> 00:48:27,487
