I can still push ahead.

866
00:48:58,560 --> 00:48:59,853
But...

867
00:49:01,063 --> 00:49:04,483
But it seems
that your extraordinary history is

868
00:49:05,442 --> 00:49:08,320
a problem
to the conservative shareholders.

869
00:49:09,279 --> 00:49:10,947
If I were to insist

870
00:49:11,031 --> 00:49:13,992
on buying the team
and guaranteeing your post as well,

871
00:49:15,160 --> 00:49:17,913
I'd probably be the only one
in the company.

872
00:49:20,290 --> 00:49:21,458
I'm used to it.

873
00:49:23,043 --> 00:49:26,004
I'm sorry. We'll see how the public
opinion goes in the future and--

